race.comment: Tricky contest. ROTAGILLA (14) failed to backup the good win two-back, when he looked a little dour through the line to finish fourth over 1800m at this track. Can race closer today and placed at the trip. Hard fit and gets every chance. UNLIMITED (11) just under a month between runs when he chipped away late for an even fifth over 1800m at this track. Expect to see him race a little closer and he represents good each way value. INQUIRING MINDS (15) returned to form off a freshen up when a plugging third over 1800m here. More effective over this distance and sure to be thereabouts again. ELLIPTICAL (3) ready to show up at his third run back with Grima's claim.
